{"tid":2256924,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我知道他不愛我 他的眼神說出他的心","createTime":"2020-10-24T17:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T04:52:31.000Z","uid":138168,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"22ba11ea5e9120e6b32b062ef4265feed0458cfc","tid":2256924,"uid":138168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T17:38:45.000Z","msg":"他不愛我 牽手的時候太冷清 擁抱的時候不夠靠近<br />\n他不愛我 說話的時候不認真 沈默的時候又太用心<br />\n<br />\n我知道他不愛我 他的眼神 說出他的心<br />\n<br />\n我看透了他的心 還有別人逗留的背影<br />\n他的回憶清除得不夠乾淨<br />\n我看到了他的心 演的全是他和她的電影<br />\n他不愛我 儘管如此 他還是贏走了我的心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n失蹤兩日都一啲唔擔心<br />\n我會靜靜消失 反正你都唔在乎"},{"pid":"1938b2f7ee862d7d6bd9b9078f5696080ad35e5c","tid":2256924,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T18:46:08.000Z","msg":"送呢首歌比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7O2ak5803mI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7O2ak5803mI&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=3b651026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7O2ak5803mI</a>"},{"pid":"2c3f2d69087cacaf5503d84365de6b3ea6163616","tid":2256924,"uid":138168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1938b2f7ee862d7d6bd9b9078f5696080ad35e5c","tid":2256924,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T18:46:08.000Z","msg":"送呢首歌比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7O2ak5803mI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7O2ak5803mI&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=3b651026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7O2ak5803mI</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T18:57:40.000Z","msg":"佢曾經唱過呢首歌俾我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm